11:36.196 --> 11:38.323
<i>so it's not actually</i>
<i>to a point.</i>

11:38.323 --> 11:39.824
<i>And then after the quench</i>

11:39.824 --> 11:41.534
<i>when I'm cleaning the rest</i>
<i>of the blade up,</i>

11:41.534 --> 11:43.077
