11:49.834 --> 11:52.503
<i>so I wanna put these teeth in</i>

11:52.503 --> 11:55.506
<i>before I heat‐treat</i>
<i>and quench the blade.</i>

11:55.506 --> 11:58.593
‐ Any sharp corners are
stress risers, right?

