is called the gullet.

12:03.932 --> 12:06.851
<i>And having a rounded gullet,</i>
<i>and putting them at an angle,</i>

12:06.851 --> 12:09.229
<i>those diagonals actually</i>
<i>wind up relieving</i>

12:09.229 --> 12:10.730
<i>those stress risers.</i>

12:10.730 --> 12:13.733
<i>‐ I don't know where</i>
<i>the angle is.</i>

12:13.733 --> 12:15.526
I don't think Mark does either.

12:15.526 --> 12:19.739
<i>‐ I don't ever put saw backs</i>
<i>in any of my knives.</i>

12:19.739 --> 12:22.283
