if I wanna saw something,

12:22.283 --> 12:25.078
and I use a knife
if I wanna cut something.

12:25.078 --> 12:27.080
<i>[rock music]</i>

12:27.080 --> 12:28.539
<i>‐ In the real world,</i>

12:28.539 --> 12:31.668
