<i>The gruesome descendant</i>
<i>of wood and stone war clubs,</i>

28:38.383 --> 28:40.510
<i>spike maces are heavy,</i>
<i>blunted weapons</i>

28:40.510 --> 28:42.971
<i>with a spherical ball</i>
