29:41.238 --> 29:44.658
<i>♪ ♪</i>

29:44.658 --> 29:47.077
<i>[tense music]</i>

29:47.077 --> 29:49.287
<i>‐ My general game plan today</i>

29:49.287 --> 29:52.207
